::KitKat::

She slowly awoke in the CR.  She didn't know how long she had been in 
there, but she had the feeling like once she stepped out, all the pit 
would break loose.  She opened the door and stepped out of the 
chamber.  She still had pain in her ribs and still felt tired, but 
the war would wait for no bot.  She walked out and looked around.
